  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Minor shelter repairs for the most vulnerable in Mosul and delivering seminars about mines and social cohesion</narrative>
  </title>
  <description type="2">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This simple project will benefit widows and orphans. This Project will be divided into two main sections.

1) Shelter repair and livelihoods (employing local people and buying materials locally)
2) Community Support through awareness raising about mines, psycho-social and support for windows with sewing machines

The project will target 1,100 residents the most vulnerable within the two of the poorest areas of East Mosul.</narrative>
  </description>
